## Findings - Prime Circle Banking
- **Hero Headline:** Get Your Compliant & Verified U.S. Business Address
- **Subheadline:** Complete Documentation Package – $2,000/Year Premium Service. We help international entrepreneurs secure a compliant U.S. business address with a real commercial lease agreement - not a virtual mailbox.
- **Pricing:** $2,000/year (billed upfront) or ~$165/month (calculated from yearly).
- **Package Details:** Real Lease Agreement, Utility Bills, Compliant Verified Address, Virtual Mailbox included.
- **Trust Signals:** 300+ Verified Leases, 100% Success Rate with Banks/Platforms, 40+ Countries Served, Founded by Max Van Beneden. Featured at Affiliate World, LeadsCon, etc.
- **CTAs:** "Join the Circle", "Secure my business", "Get Access to US Business Address", "Telegram" (t.me/max_fbsolutionprovider).
- **Comparison Table:** Compares "Not Compliant" (Home, Virtual, PO Box, Co-working) vs "Fully Compliant" (Real physical, Lease, Utility bill).
- **Key Messaging:** "Real commercial lease agreement - not a virtual mailbox", "100% Compliance Ready", "Stay Protected".
- **FAQ Topics:** What's included, Why $2k/year, Compliance, Setup speed (1-2 days), Documents received, States available.
- **Design Style:** Dark navy (#0A1C3F), Gold (#D4AF37), White. High-end, fintech feel.
- **USPs:** Real commercial lease (not virtual), includes utility bills, guaranteed bank approval, fast 1-2 day setup, direct Telegram access to founder/team.
